data.description: Welcome to your home in Brooklyn Park. This charming residence is conveniently located near schools, shopping centers and parks, offering both convenience and recreation. With a tastefully redone interior in 2006 featuring updated kitchen, updated baths, hardwood floors and three bedrooms on one level, this home is perfect for modern living. The lower level adds even more space with a fourth bedroom, office, and a spacious family room. Step outside to enjoy the private backyard oasis, ideal for relaxation and gatherings. Agents and buyers verify all measurement. Don't miss this well-priced opportunity to make this your perfect home!
